00:44:22,678 --> 00:44:23,679
(CHATTAR SCOFFS)

529
00:44:24,597 --> 00:44:26,849
You see, Captain, a rock!

530
00:44:28,350 --> 00:44:30,019
(ALL EXCLAIMING)

531
00:44:33,606 --> 00:44:35,024
(INHALING)

532
00:44:37,860 --> 00:44:39,486
(SCREAMING)

533
00:44:39,570 --> 00:44:40,863
(WHIMPERING)

534
00:44:42,198 --> 00:44:46,035
Something connected the villagers' rock

535
00:44:46,535 --> 00:44:49,205
and the old legend
of the Sankara Stones.

536
00:44:49,288 --> 00:44:53,542
CHATTAR: Dr. Jones, we are
all vulnerable to vicious rumors.

537
00:44:53,959 --> 00:44:56,212
I seem to remember that in Honduras

538
00:44:56,295 --> 00:44:58,339
you were accused of being
a grave robber

539
00:44:58,422 --> 00:45:00,132
rather than an archeologist.

540
00:45:00,216 --> 00:45:03,552
Well, the newspapers greatly
exaggerated the incident.

541
00:45:03,636 --> 00:45:06,889
And wasn't it the Sultan of Madagascar
who threatened to cut your head off

542
00:45:06,972 --> 00:45:08,307
if you ever returned to his country?

543
00:45:08,390 --> 00:45:09,433
No, it wasn't my head.

544
00:45:09,516 --> 00:45:10,809
Then your hands, perhaps.

545
00:45:10,893 --> 00:45:12,895
No, it wasn't my hands,

546
00:45:12,978 --> 00:45:14,063
it was my...

547
00:45:15,439 --> 00:45:16,732
My misunderstanding.

548
00:45:16,815 --> 00:45:19,109
Exactly what we have here, Dr. Jones.

549
00:45:19,193 --> 00:45:22,154
MAHARAJAH: I have heard
the evil stories of the Thuggee cult.

550
00:45:22,238 --> 00:45:23,239
(MUSIC STOPS)

551
00:45:23,322 --> 00:45:26,408
I thought the stories were told
to frighten children.

552
00:45:27,034 --> 00:45:30,162
Later, I learnt
the Thuggee cult was once real

553
00:45:30,246 --> 00:45:32,581
and did of unspeakable things.

554
00:45:33,082 --> 00:45:36,669
I am ashamed of what happened here
so many years ago,

555
00:45:36,752 --> 00:45:38,087
and I assure you

556
00:45:38,170 --> 00:45:42,258
this will never happen again
in my kingdom.

557
00:45:43,092 --> 00:45:45,010
If I offended you,

558
00:45:46,262 --> 00:45:47,721
then I am sorry.

559
00:45:48,430 --> 00:45:50,057
(MUSIC CONTINUES)

560
00:45:58,732 --> 00:46:00,609
Dessert!

561
00:46:13,289 --> 00:46:15,624
Chilled monkey brains.

562
00:46:19,503 --> 00:46:21,964
(MOANING)

563
00:46:22,631 --> 00:46:23,674
(THUDDING)

564
00:46:24,466 --> 00:46:25,467
(YAWNS)

565
00:46:31,056 --> 00:46:33,058
I think I'll just check on Willie.

566
00:46:34,601 --> 00:46:36,562
That's all you better do.

567
00:46:38,689 --> 00:46:40,816
Tell me later what happened.

568
00:46:40,899 --> 00:46:42,568
Am-scray.

569
00:46:53,495 --> 00:46:55,164
I've got something for you.

570
00:46:55,664 --> 00:46:59,501
There's nothing you have
that I could possibly want.

571
00:46:59,585 --> 00:47:01,045
Right.

572
00:47:08,677 --> 00:47:10,012
(MOANING)

573
00:47:13,974 --> 00:47:15,893
You're a very nice man.

574
00:47:15,976 --> 00:47:18,645
Maybe you could be my palace slave.

575
00:47:28,530 --> 00:47:30,949
Wear your jewels to bed, Princess?

576
00:47:31,700 --> 00:47:33,077
Yeah.

577
00:47:34,953 --> 00:47:36,205
And nothing else.

578
00:47:37,039 --> 00:47:38,207
That shock you?

579
00:47:38,290 --> 00:47:39,958
Nothing shocks me.

580
00:47:40,709 --> 00:47:42,628
I'm a scientist.

581
00:47:43,796 --> 00:47:46,507
So, as a scientist,
you do a lot of research?

582
00:47:47,633 --> 00:47:48,967
Always.

583
00:47:49,259 --> 00:47:51,553
And what sort of research
would you do on me?

584
00:47:55,182 --> 00:47:56,558
Nocturnal activities.

585
00:47:56,642 --> 00:47:59,686
You mean like what sort of cream
I put on my face at night,

586
00:47:59,770 --> 00:48:01,438
what position I like to sleep in?

587
00:48:01,647 --> 00:48:02,981
Mating customs.

588
00:48:03,065 --> 00:48:04,108
Love rituals?

589
00:48:04,400 --> 00:48:07,111
Primitive sexual practices.

590
00:48:07,194 --> 00:48:08,904
So you're an authority in that area?

591
00:48:09,238 --> 00:48:10,656
Years of fieldwork.

592
00:48:20,290 --> 00:48:22,751
I don't blame you for being sore at me.

593
00:48:23,085 --> 00:48:25,504
I can be hard to handle.

594
00:48:26,422 --> 00:48:28,215
I've had worse.

595
00:48:28,841 --> 00:48:31,051
But you'll never have better.

596
00:48:34,012 --> 00:48:35,722
I don't know.

597
00:48:35,806 --> 00:48:38,058
As a scientist,
I don't want to prejudice my experiment.

598
00:48:38,142 --> 00:48:39,810
I'll let you know in the morning.

599
00:48:40,894 --> 00:48:43,480
Why, you conceited ape.

600
00:48:43,564 --> 00:48:45,816
I'm not that easy.

601
00:48:47,484 --> 00:48:49,528
I'm not that easy, either.

602
00:48:50,112 --> 00:48:51,655
Trouble with you is, Willie,

603
00:48:51,738 --> 00:48:53,949
you're too used to getting your own way.

604
00:48:54,783 --> 00:48:56,034
And you're just too proud to admit

605
00:48:56,118 --> 00:48:59,288
that you're crazy about me, Dr. Jones.

606
00:48:59,788 --> 00:49:02,833
If you want me, Willie,
you know where you can find me.

607
00:49:03,417 --> 00:49:04,877
Five minutes.

608
00:49:04,960 --> 00:49:06,962
You'll be back over here in five minutes.

609
00:49:07,045 --> 00:49:08,589
I'll be asleep in five minutes.

610
00:49:08,672 --> 00:49:09,882
Five.

611
00:49:09,965 --> 00:49:12,301
You know it, and I know it.

612
00:49:26,982 --> 00:49:28,984
Five minutes.

613
00:49:31,153 --> 00:49:33,155
Four and a half.

614
00:49:48,504 --> 00:49:49,546
(SNIFFING)

615
00:50:04,353 --> 00:50:05,854
(CLOCK TICKING)

616
00:50:22,704 --> 00:50:23,830
(GASPS)

617
00:50:26,959 --> 00:50:29,211
(CHUCKLES) "Palace slave."

618
00:50:29,586 --> 00:50:31,838
"Nocturnal activities."

619
00:50:33,507 --> 00:50:35,384
I'm a "conceited ape"? (SCOFFS)

620
00:50:36,134 --> 00:50:37,469
"I'll tell you in the morning."

621
00:50:39,429 --> 00:50:41,098
I can't believe it.

622
00:50:41,473 --> 00:50:42,724
He's not coming.

623
00:50:43,183 --> 00:50:44,810
She's not coming.

624
00:50:47,145 --> 00:50:48,397
I can't believe I'm not going.

625
00:50:48,480 --> 00:50:49,565
(GRUNTS)

626
00:50:51,525 --> 00:50:52,943
(GRUNTING)

627
00:51:08,875 --> 00:51:10,419
Indiana Jones!

628
00:51:10,502 --> 00:51:13,171
This is one night you'll never forget!

629
00:51:13,255 --> 00:51:16,341
This is the night
I slipped right through your fingers!

630
00:51:18,468 --> 00:51:19,720
Sleep tight,

631
00:51:19,803 --> 00:51:21,471
and pleasant dreams!

632
00:51:21,597 --> 00:51:22,639
(CHOKING)

633
00:51:24,433 --> 00:51:27,060
I could have been
your greatest adventure.

634
00:51:30,772 --> 00:51:31,857
(CRASHING)

635
00:51:32,024 --> 00:51:33,108
(GASPS)

636
00:51:37,654 --> 00:51:38,780
Dr. Jones, your whip!

637
00:51:47,456 --> 00:51:48,582
(GROANS)

638
00:52:00,302 --> 00:52:01,386
Shorty,

639
00:52:01,470 --> 00:52:02,596
turn off the switch.

640
00:52:09,102 --> 00:52:10,354
Oh, Indy.

641
00:52:11,605 --> 00:52:12,689
Be gentle with me.

642
00:52:12,773 --> 00:52:14,441
Be gentle with me.

643
00:52:20,280 --> 00:52:22,240
But I'm here.

644
00:52:33,960 --> 00:52:35,003
There's nobody here.

645
00:52:35,337 --> 00:52:37,339
No, I'm here.

646
00:52:38,340 --> 00:52:41,134
Indy, you're acting awfully strange.

647
00:53:07,035 --> 00:53:09,996
Hey, I'm right here.

648
00:53:10,831 --> 00:53:11,915
(SCREAMS)

649
00:53:22,092 --> 00:53:26,346
"Follow in the footsteps of Siva."

650
00:53:26,555 --> 00:53:28,348
WILLIE: What does that mean?

651
00:53:31,476 --> 00:53:34,730
"Do not betray these truths."

652
00:53:34,813 --> 00:53:37,399
Shorty, go get our stuff.

653
00:53:38,316 --> 00:53:39,818
(WILLIE MOANS)

654
00:54:06,428 --> 00:54:08,597
INDY: Stay behind me, Short Round.

655
00:54:09,556 --> 00:54:13,185
Step where I step,
and don't touch anything.

656
00:54:19,733 --> 00:54:21,109
(SHORTY SCREAMS)

657
00:54:22,110 --> 00:54:23,779
(PANTING HEAVILY)

658
00:54:25,697 --> 00:54:27,157
I step where you step.

659
00:54:27,240 --> 00:54:29,201
I touch nothing.

660
00:54:30,452 --> 00:54:32,454
Indy!

661
00:54:51,556 --> 00:54:53,016
(CRUNCHING)

662
00:54:53,141 --> 00:54:54,935
SHORTY: I step on something.

663
00:54:56,061 --> 00:54:58,313
INDY: Yeah,
there's something on the ground.

664
00:54:58,396 --> 00:55:00,732
SHORTY: Feel like
step on fortune cookies.

665
00:55:01,942 --> 00:55:04,528
INDY: It's not fortune cookies.

666
00:55:06,196 --> 00:55:08,323
Let me take a look.

667
00:55:12,327 --> 00:55:14,621
(RATTLING)

668
00:55:18,792 --> 00:55:20,126
(SCREECHING)

669
00:55:21,711 --> 00:55:23,380
(PANTING) That's no cookies.

670
00:55:24,047 --> 00:55:25,841
INDY: It's all right. I got him.

671
00:55:29,177 --> 00:55:31,137
Go. There, go.

672
00:55:39,688 --> 00:55:40,772
(RUMBLING)

673
00:56:11,094 --> 00:56:12,178
Stop.

674
00:56:12,262 --> 00:56:15,515
Look, just stand up against the wall,
will you?

675
00:56:22,856 --> 00:56:24,858
(RUMBLING)

676
00:56:26,359 --> 00:56:27,402
(GASPS)

677
00:56:27,485 --> 00:56:29,404
(RUMBLING CONTINUES)

678
00:56:30,488 --> 00:56:32,657
You say to stand against the wall!

679
00:56:32,741 --> 00:56:34,075
I listen to what you say!

680
00:56:34,159 --> 00:56:36,244
- Not my fault! Not my fault!
- Willie, get down here!

681
00:56:36,328 --> 00:56:38,204
We're in trouble!

682
00:56:38,455 --> 00:56:41,166
Willie! Willie!

683
00:56:41,249 --> 00:56:43,835
Bet I get all dirty again.

684
00:56:44,294 --> 00:56:45,837
- Willie, get down here!
- Not my fault!

685
00:56:45,921 --> 00:56:47,005
We're in trouble!

686
00:56:47,505 --> 00:56:50,342
Trouble? Trouble? What sort of...

687
00:56:50,425 --> 00:56:52,969
(SCREAMING)

688
00:57:05,815 --> 00:57:07,442
This is serious!

689
00:57:07,609 --> 00:57:10,904
There are two dead people down here!

690
00:57:11,154 --> 00:57:14,240
There're going to be
two dead people in here! Hurry!

691
00:57:14,449 --> 00:57:16,493
I've almost had enough of you two.

692
00:57:16,785 --> 00:57:17,827
Willie!

693
00:57:17,953 --> 00:57:19,621
What's the rush?

694
00:57:19,829 --> 00:57:22,916
It's a long story, Willie.
Hurry, or you don't get to hear it.

695
00:57:25,001 --> 00:57:27,712
God, what is this?

696
00:57:29,631 --> 00:57:31,257
Indy, what is this?

697
00:57:31,341 --> 00:57:33,635
I can't see a thing!

698
00:57:34,469 --> 00:57:35,553
Hurry!

699
00:57:35,637 --> 00:57:37,263
All right!

700
00:57:37,347 --> 00:57:38,807
Oh, I broke a nail.

701
00:57:48,233 --> 00:57:50,443
(RATTLING)

702
00:57:51,653 --> 00:57:53,113
(SCREAMING)

703
00:57:53,363 --> 00:57:54,906
Willie, hurry!

704
00:57:54,990 --> 00:57:56,992
WILLIE: They're in my hair!

705
00:57:57,075 --> 00:57:58,827
INDY: Shut up, Willie!

706
00:58:00,120 --> 00:58:02,622
- Indy, let me in!
- SHORTY: No, let us out!

707
00:58:02,706 --> 00:58:04,749
- Let me in!
- Let us out!

708
00:58:04,833 --> 00:58:06,543
- INDY: Shut up!
- I'm down here!

709
00:58:06,626 --> 00:58:08,003
They're all over me!

710
00:58:08,753 --> 00:58:11,423
There's got to be
a fulcrum release lever somewhere.

711
00:58:11,506 --> 00:58:12,507
What?

712
00:58:12,674 --> 00:58:14,509
A handle that opens the door.

713
00:58:14,718 --> 00:58:16,428
- Go on!
- They're just, just square holes!

714
00:58:16,511 --> 00:58:18,096
INDY: Go to the right hole.

715
00:58:19,347 --> 00:58:20,807
SHORTY: Hurry, Willie!

716
00:58:22,475 --> 00:58:23,852
(GROANING IN DISGUST)

717
00:58:25,478 --> 00:58:27,522
(SCREAMING)

718
00:58:27,689 --> 00:58:30,692
INDY: The other one! The other right.
Your other right!

719
00:58:30,775 --> 00:58:33,194
- The one on your right!
- There's slime inside!

720
00:58:33,778 --> 00:58:35,155
I can't do it.

721
00:58:35,488 --> 00:58:37,282
You can do it. Feel inside.

722
00:58:37,574 --> 00:58:38,700
Okay.

723
00:58:39,868 --> 00:58:41,369
(RATTLING)

724
00:58:42,203 --> 00:58:43,371
You feel inside!

725
00:58:44,039 --> 00:58:45,331
Do it now!

726
00:58:45,415 --> 00:58:46,791
Okay!

727
00:58:47,751 --> 00:58:49,544
(RUMBLING)

728
00:58:55,967 --> 00:59:00,555
Willie, we are going to die!

729
00:59:01,890 --> 00:59:03,308
WILLIE: It's soft.

730
00:59:06,227 --> 00:59:07,479
It's moving!

731
00:59:07,979 --> 00:59:09,814
(RATTLING)

732
00:59:15,653 --> 00:59:16,696
Got it!

733
00:59:31,419 --> 00:59:33,338
Get 'em off of me! Get 'em off of me!

734
00:59:33,546 --> 00:59:36,257
They're all over me! Get 'em off me!

735
00:59:38,927 --> 00:59:40,220
No!

736
00:59:42,347 --> 00:59:44,057
It wasn't me! It's her!

737
00:59:44,140 --> 00:59:45,141
Huh?

738
00:59:46,184 --> 00:59:47,352
Come on!

739
00:59:47,435 --> 00:59:50,647
Go! Move! Come on, move! Come on!

740
01:00:20,552 --> 01:00:22,428
(CHANTING)

741
01:00:44,909 --> 01:00:46,411
(DRUM BEATING)

742
01:00:47,078 --> 01:00:48,663
(CHANTING CONTINUES)

743
01:00:51,499 --> 01:00:53,585
It's a Thuggee ceremony.

744
01:00:53,668 --> 01:00:55,170
They're worshipping Kali.

745
01:01:04,721 --> 01:01:07,390
Have you ever seen anything
like this before?

746
01:01:07,473 --> 01:01:09,684
Nobody's seen this for a hundred years.

747
01:01:32,916 --> 01:01:35,043
(CHANTING)

748
01:01:51,476 --> 01:01:53,978
(MAN SPEAKING HINDI)

749
01:02:09,494 --> 01:02:11,329
(MAN CHANTING)

750
01:02:32,225 --> 01:02:35,687
(SPEAKING HINDI)

751
01:02:44,779 --> 01:02:49,492
Kali Ma. Kali Ma...

752
01:02:50,410 --> 01:02:51,619
Kali Ma!

753
01:02:56,040 --> 01:02:58,418
(HEART BEATING)

754
01:03:04,299 --> 01:03:05,383
(SCREAMING)

755
01:03:11,347 --> 01:03:12,557
- (SCREAMING)
- (GASPS)

756
01:03:13,266 --> 01:03:15,393
(MOLA SPEAKING IN HINDI)

757
01:03:18,313 --> 01:03:20,565
(ALL CHEERING)

758
01:03:28,781 --> 01:03:30,116
He's still alive.

759
01:03:30,241 --> 01:03:31,743
(CHANTING)

760
01:03:33,328 --> 01:03:34,829
(GASPING)

761
01:04:06,444 --> 01:04:08,154
(SCREAMING)

762
01:04:36,557 --> 01:04:38,434
(LAUGHING MANIACALLY)

763
01:04:54,909 --> 01:04:56,702
Kali Ma.

764
01:05:24,856 --> 01:05:26,607
(CHEERING)

765
01:05:58,055 --> 01:06:01,225
That's the rock
they took from the village.

766
01:06:01,309 --> 01:06:03,811
It's one of the Sankara Stones.

767
01:06:11,068 --> 01:06:12,195
Why they glow like that?

768
01:06:12,278 --> 01:06:13,571
(SHUSHING)

769
01:06:15,031 --> 01:06:16,616
The legend says

770
01:06:16,699 --> 01:06:17,950
when the rocks are brought together,

771
01:06:18,034 --> 01:06:20,411
the diamonds inside them will glow.

772
01:06:21,078 --> 01:06:22,121
Diamonds?

773
01:06:22,205 --> 01:06:23,289
Diamonds.

774
01:06:23,372 --> 01:06:24,582
- Diamonds!
- Shh!

775
01:06:24,665 --> 01:06:25,708
Diamonds.

776
01:06:42,808 --> 01:06:44,101
Hey, hey.

777
01:06:44,185 --> 01:06:47,939
Look, I want you two
to stay up here and keep quiet.

778
01:06:48,022 --> 01:06:49,357
Shorty, you keep an eye on her.

779
01:06:49,440 --> 01:06:51,150
- Why, where are you going?
- Down there.

780
01:06:51,234 --> 01:06:54,278
Down there? Are you crazy?

781
01:06:54,362 --> 01:06:57,490
I'm not leaving here without the stones.

782
01:06:57,573 --> 01:07:00,785
You could get killed chasing after
your damn fortune and glory!

783
01:07:00,868 --> 01:07:01,869
Maybe.

784
01:07:03,454 --> 01:07:05,373
But not today.

785
01:08:20,573 --> 01:08:22,408
(MOUTHING) Be careful.

786
01:08:55,900 --> 01:08:57,818
(SCREAMING IN DISTANCE)

787
01:09:32,186 --> 01:09:34,021
Where's he going?

788
01:09:34,814 --> 01:09:36,440
(SCREAMING)

789
01:09:36,524 --> 01:09:38,567
Let me go!

790
01:09:41,529 --> 01:09:43,906
Run, Willie! Run!

791
01:10:14,145 --> 01:10:16,272
(SPEAKING HINDI)

792
01:10:19,859 --> 01:10:20,943
(GROWLING)

793
01:10:34,248 --> 01:10:37,001
(SPEAKING HINDI)

794
01:11:17,792 --> 01:11:19,376
Dr. Jones!

795
01:11:21,670 --> 01:11:23,047
I keep telling you,

796
01:11:23,130 --> 01:11:26,175
you listen me more, you live longer.

797
01:11:26,300 --> 01:11:28,636
BOY: Please, let me die.

798
01:11:30,429 --> 01:11:31,597
I pray to Siva,

799
01:11:32,264 --> 01:11:35,434
"Let me die," but I do not.

800
01:11:35,976 --> 01:11:38,854
Now... Now the evil of Kali take me.

801
01:11:40,523 --> 01:11:41,690
How?

802
01:11:41,774 --> 01:11:44,568
They will make me drink
the blood of the Kali.

803
01:11:44,652 --> 01:11:47,988
Then I'll fall into
the Black Sleep of the Kali Ma.

804
01:11:48,280 --> 01:11:49,448
What is that?

805
01:11:50,533 --> 01:11:51,867
We become like them.

806
01:11:54,411 --> 01:11:58,207
We'll be alive, but like a nightmare.

807
01:11:58,290 --> 01:12:01,794
You drink blood,
you not wake up from nightmare.

808
01:12:13,639 --> 01:12:17,518
You were caught trying to steal
the Sankara Stones.

809
01:12:18,352 --> 01:12:20,688
There were five stones in the beginning.

810
01:12:21,522 --> 01:12:24,441
Over the centuries,
they were dispersed by wars,

811
01:12:24,525 --> 01:12:26,652
sold off by thieves like you.

812
01:12:26,735 --> 01:12:28,153
Thieves like me, huh?

813
01:12:28,237 --> 01:12:29,321
(SCOFFS)

814
01:12:30,030 --> 01:12:32,408
Still missing two.

815
01:12:33,117 --> 01:12:35,369
A century ago,
when the British raided this temple

816
01:12:35,452 --> 01:12:37,329
and butchered my people,

817
01:12:37,413 --> 01:12:41,792
a loyal priest hid the last two stones
down here in the catacombs.

818
01:12:41,876 --> 01:12:45,045
So that's what you've got
these slaves digging for, huh?

819
01:12:45,629 --> 01:12:46,964
They're innocent children.

820
01:12:47,047 --> 01:12:49,800
They dig for the gems
to support our cause.

821
01:12:51,260 --> 01:12:53,929
They also search
for the last two stones.

822
01:12:56,390 --> 01:12:59,977
Soon we will have
all the five Sankara Stones,

823
01:13:00,060 --> 01:13:02,938
and the Thuggees will be all powerful.

824
01:13:03,480 --> 01:13:06,150
What a vivid imagination.

825
01:13:06,233 --> 01:13:07,776
(MOLA LAUGHING)

826
01:13:11,238 --> 01:13:14,325
You don't believe me?

827
01:13:15,701 --> 01:13:18,203
You will, Dr. Jones.

828
01:13:20,247 --> 01:13:24,793
You will become a true believer.

829
01:13:24,877 --> 01:13:27,046
(BOTH LAUGHING)

830
01:13:29,882 --> 01:13:31,467
(GATE CREAKING)

831
01:13:42,102 --> 01:13:43,479
Hi.

832
01:14:01,497 --> 01:14:04,667
(SPEAKING HINDI)

833
01:14:07,962 --> 01:14:09,213
SHORTY: Dr. Jones!

834
01:14:09,296 --> 01:14:10,756
Don't drink, it's bad!

835
01:14:10,839 --> 01:14:12,841
Don't drink!

836
01:14:12,925 --> 01:14:14,343
Spit it out!

837
01:14:17,721 --> 01:14:20,099
(SPEAKING HINDI)

838
01:14:40,035 --> 01:14:41,370
(GROANING)

839
01:14:43,914 --> 01:14:46,083
(GROANING)

840
01:14:48,252 --> 01:14:50,087
Dr. Jones... (SPEAKING CHINESE)

841
01:14:52,089 --> 01:14:54,550
(SPEAKING HINDI)

842
01:15:01,181 --> 01:15:02,599
(SHOUTING IN CHINESE)

843
01:15:07,855 --> 01:15:11,483
You dare not do that.

844
01:15:16,280 --> 01:15:18,032
(SPEAKING HINDI)

845
01:15:27,875 --> 01:15:28,959
(SCREAMS)

846
01:15:29,835 --> 01:15:31,712
Leave him alone, you bastards!

847
01:15:42,431 --> 01:15:44,641
The British in India will be slaughtered.

848
01:15:44,725 --> 01:15:46,977
Then we will overrun the Muslims.

849
01:15:47,061 --> 01:15:49,813
Then the Hebrew God will fall.

850
01:15:50,606 --> 01:15:53,525
And then the Christian God
will be cast down and forgotten.

851
01:15:53,609 --> 01:15:54,818
(CHOKING)

852
01:15:56,070 --> 01:15:59,156
Soon, Kali Ma will rule the world.

853
01:16:00,449 --> 01:16:01,575
(COUGHING)

854
01:16:05,621 --> 01:16:07,581
Dr. Jones...

855
01:16:20,302 --> 01:16:22,638
(GASPING)

856
01:16:25,474 --> 01:16:26,975
(GROANING LOUDLY)

857
01:16:27,059 --> 01:16:28,310
(ECHOING)

858
01:17:04,763 --> 01:17:07,850
(LAUGHING)

859
01:17:10,561 --> 01:17:12,771
(CROWS CAWING)

860
01:17:17,484 --> 01:17:18,861
(SPEAKS HINDI)

861
01:17:23,740 --> 01:17:25,450
(SPEAKS HINDI)

862
01:17:40,966 --> 01:17:43,051
(SPEAKING HINDI)

863
01:17:50,976 --> 01:17:53,854
Kali Ma protects us.

864
01:17:53,937 --> 01:17:56,106
We are her children.

865
01:17:57,316 --> 01:17:59,443
We pledge our devotion to her

866
01:17:59,526 --> 01:18:01,445
with an offering of flesh...

867
01:18:01,528 --> 01:18:03,322
WILLIE: What are you doing?

868
01:18:06,200 --> 01:18:08,368
...and blood.

869
01:18:17,377 --> 01:18:21,715
Your friend has seen,
and she has heard.

870
01:18:22,841 --> 01:18:25,719
Now she will not talk.

871
01:18:35,062 --> 01:18:36,855
I'm not going to have
anything nice to say

872
01:18:36,939 --> 01:18:38,815
about this place when I get back.

873
01:18:39,107 --> 01:18:42,486
Indy! For God sakes, help me!

874
01:18:42,569 --> 01:18:44,780
What's the matter with you?

875
01:18:44,863 --> 01:18:45,948
(WILLIE SOBBING)

876
01:18:47,950 --> 01:18:49,618
(MEN CHANTING)

877
01:18:59,920 --> 01:19:02,631
No, no.

878
01:19:03,173 --> 01:19:06,301
(SPEAKING HINDI)

879
01:19:33,620 --> 01:19:35,163
MOLA: Come.

880
01:19:37,749 --> 01:19:39,251
Come.

881
01:20:01,773 --> 01:20:03,650
Indiana...

882
01:20:05,152 --> 01:20:08,655
Indiana, help us.

883
01:20:22,294 --> 01:20:24,588
Please, snap out of it.

884
01:20:25,839 --> 01:20:28,342
(SOBBING) You're not one of them.

885
01:20:30,385 --> 01:20:32,596
You're not one of them.

886
01:20:35,640 --> 01:20:37,726
Please come back to us.

887
01:20:38,518 --> 01:20:40,520
Don't leave me.

888
01:20:52,657 --> 01:20:53,992
(CHANTING IN HINDI)

889
01:20:54,076 --> 01:20:55,786
(SCREAMING) No!

890
01:20:58,830 --> 01:21:01,041
What are you doing?

891
01:21:01,124 --> 01:21:02,834
Are you mad?

892
01:21:03,794 --> 01:21:05,921
(CHANTING IN HINDI)

893
01:21:10,258 --> 01:21:11,510
(SPITS)

894
01:21:20,894 --> 01:21:22,646
(CONTINUES CHANTING)

895
01:21:36,535 --> 01:21:38,120
(ALL SHOUTING)

896
01:21:41,123 --> 01:21:42,707
(SHOUTING IN HINDI)

897
01:22:19,494 --> 01:22:22,122
This can't be happening,
this can't be happening.

898
01:22:22,747 --> 01:22:25,834
Wake up, Willie, wake up.

899
01:22:41,141 --> 01:22:43,310
(SCREAMING)

900
01:22:56,948 --> 01:22:59,826
No! No! No!

901
01:23:11,838 --> 01:23:13,757
No, no, no!

902
01:23:14,466 --> 01:23:16,801
Wake up, Dr. Jones, wake up!

903
01:23:21,014 --> 01:23:22,807
Dr. Jones!

904
01:23:23,391 --> 01:23:24,559
(COMMANDS IN HINDI)

905
01:23:30,774 --> 01:23:32,150
(GROANING)

906
01:23:38,365 --> 01:23:39,866
Indy, I love you.

907
01:23:41,243 --> 01:23:42,369
Wake up, Indy! Wake up!

908
01:23:42,452 --> 01:23:43,870
(SCREAMS)

909
01:23:46,039 --> 01:23:49,167
You're my best friend! Wake up, Indy!

910
01:23:54,422 --> 01:23:56,424
Wait! Wait!

911
01:23:57,217 --> 01:23:58,843
He's mine!

912
01:24:02,305 --> 01:24:04,599
I'm all right, kid.

913
01:24:12,399 --> 01:24:14,025
(ALL CLAMORING)

914
01:24:49,102 --> 01:24:50,312
Mola Ram!

915
01:24:50,937 --> 01:24:52,772
(LAUGHING MANIACALLY)

916
01:25:25,305 --> 01:25:26,806
(GRUNTING)

917
01:25:32,103 --> 01:25:33,521
(CHATTAR LAUGHING)

918
01:25:47,535 --> 01:25:48,953
(MOANING)

919
01:26:06,971 --> 01:26:08,598
(ALL CLAMORING)

920
01:26:12,352 --> 01:26:14,270
Give me some slack!

921
01:26:30,036 --> 01:26:31,121
(WILLIE MOANS)

922
01:26:33,331 --> 01:26:36,084
Willie, Willie, wake up!

923
01:26:38,086 --> 01:26:40,630
Willie, Willie, it's me! I'm back!

924
01:26:43,341 --> 01:26:45,135
Oh, Indy.

925
01:27:13,037 --> 01:27:15,206
Indy, my friend.

926
01:27:16,291 --> 01:27:18,251
I'm sorry, kid.

927
01:27:24,966 --> 01:27:27,886
Indy, now, let's get out of here.

928
01:27:30,680 --> 01:27:33,099
Right. All of us.

929
01:27:35,935 --> 01:27:37,103
(SPEAKING HINDI)

930
01:27:56,122 --> 01:27:58,124
(ALL SHOUTING)

931
01:28:11,346 --> 01:28:13,973
(CHILDREN CLAMORING)

932
01:28:46,631 --> 01:28:48,216
WILLIE: No!

933
01:29:04,732 --> 01:29:05,859
I've got to save him!

934
01:29:05,942 --> 01:29:08,194
- He can take care of himself.
- He needs me.

935
01:29:09,112 --> 01:29:10,363
(MOANS)

936
01:29:10,905 --> 01:29:12,115
I've got to save Indy!

937
01:29:24,460 --> 01:29:26,880
Okay, save him.

938
01:29:30,550 --> 01:29:31,968
Drop him down!

939
01:29:32,051 --> 01:29:34,262
I kill you! Drop him down!

940
01:30:01,414 --> 01:30:02,916
(MOANING)

941
01:30:05,543 --> 01:30:07,086
What's the matter with him?

942
01:30:09,839 --> 01:30:10,924
(MOANING)

943
01:30:50,380 --> 01:30:52,465
Here. Try this.

944
01:31:22,578 --> 01:31:24,247
(SCREAMING)

945
01:31:37,885 --> 01:31:38,886
(LAUGHS)

946
01:31:57,405 --> 01:31:58,823
(SCREAMING)

947
01:32:07,290 --> 01:32:09,208
Go, Indy!

948
01:32:34,567 --> 01:32:35,943
(SCREAMING)

949
01:32:38,905 --> 01:32:41,407
(PLEADING IN HINDI)

950
01:32:55,129 --> 01:32:56,255
(EXCLAIMS IN DISGUST)

951
01:32:57,757 --> 01:32:58,841
(SCREAMS)

952
01:33:05,056 --> 01:33:06,099
(SCREAMS)

953
01:33:11,395 --> 01:33:13,731
It was the Black Sleep of Kali.

954
01:33:26,953 --> 01:33:28,162
Short Round!

955
01:33:29,330 --> 01:33:32,458
Quit fooling around with that kid!
Get down in the cart, now!

956
01:33:32,834 --> 01:33:34,043
Okeydokey, Indy!

957
01:33:34,585 --> 01:33:37,463
Please listen.
To get out, you must take the left tunnel.

958
01:33:37,797 --> 01:33:39,173
Thank you.

959
01:33:49,433 --> 01:33:50,434
(SCREAMS)

960
01:34:26,971 --> 01:34:28,431
Shorty! Quit stalling!

961
01:34:28,681 --> 01:34:29,765
(COMMANDING IN HINDI)

962
01:34:29,849 --> 01:34:30,850
SHORTY: Come on, Indy!

963
01:34:30,933 --> 01:34:32,018
Go!

964
01:34:32,351 --> 01:34:33,477
Go! Go!

965
01:34:36,981 --> 01:34:38,858
Shorty, look out!

966
01:34:46,407 --> 01:34:48,451
- Come on!
- Indy!

967
01:34:53,915 --> 01:34:54,916
Hurry!

968
01:35:00,213 --> 01:35:02,131
Hurry! Hurry up!

969
01:35:05,051 --> 01:35:07,637
(ORDERING IN HINDI)

970
01:35:07,762 --> 01:35:11,140
SHORTY: Indy, take the left tunnel!
The left tunnel!

971
01:35:11,224 --> 01:35:13,976
No, Indy! You missed it! Left tunnel!

972
01:35:41,754 --> 01:35:42,922
(GUNSHOTS)

973
01:35:44,924 --> 01:35:46,676
We got company!

974
01:35:50,972 --> 01:35:52,723
- Stop.
- Let her go!

975
01:35:52,807 --> 01:35:54,600
- Let go of the brake.
- What?

976
01:35:54,976 --> 01:35:56,477
- What?
- Let her go.

977
01:35:56,560 --> 01:35:57,979
Our only chance is to outrun them.

978
01:36:15,037 --> 01:36:16,163
- Shorty?
- Huh?

979
01:36:16,247 --> 01:36:18,249
Come up here and take the brake.

980
01:36:19,292 --> 01:36:21,961
Watch it on the curves,
or we'll fly right off the track.

981
01:36:22,044 --> 01:36:23,296
SHORTY: Okay.

982
01:37:05,129 --> 01:37:06,130
(SCREAMING)

983
01:37:19,310 --> 01:37:20,686
(CHEERING)

984
01:37:22,646 --> 01:37:24,023
(GUNSHOTS)

985
01:37:29,362 --> 01:37:31,530
(ORDERING IN HINDI)

986
01:37:44,710 --> 01:37:46,796
- What are you doing?
- Short cut.

987
01:37:46,879 --> 01:37:48,422
- Yes, Indy.
- Short, cut.

988
01:38:12,738 --> 01:38:14,407
INDY: Watch it.

989
01:38:18,369 --> 01:38:19,870
SHORTY: Indy, help!

990
01:38:22,998 --> 01:38:24,291
- WILLIE: Hang on!
- Indy!

991
01:38:25,126 --> 01:38:27,586
WILLIE: Pull him in.
SHORTY: Let me go! Let me go!

992
01:38:28,963 --> 01:38:30,673
Let go of him!

993
01:38:31,674 --> 01:38:34,051
SHORTY: No! No!

994
01:38:34,135 --> 01:38:35,177
WILLIE: Pull him in!

995
01:38:35,261 --> 01:38:36,345
- I'll catch him!
- No!

996
01:39:11,755 --> 01:39:13,048
(SCREAMS)

997
01:39:21,098 --> 01:39:22,933
(SCREAMING)

998
01:39:23,017 --> 01:39:23,642
Duck!

999
01:39:43,954 --> 01:39:45,039
INDY: All right.
SHORTY: What?

1000
01:39:45,122 --> 01:39:46,707
INDY: Brakes. Brakes.

1001
01:39:46,790 --> 01:39:48,751
- Slow us down.
- SHORTY: Okay.

1002
01:39:54,006 --> 01:39:56,509
Big mistake. Big mistake, Indy.

1003
01:39:56,592 --> 01:39:57,676
WILLIE: Figures.

1004
01:40:18,948 --> 01:40:20,449
We're going too fast!

1005
01:40:20,533 --> 01:40:21,617
Too fast!

1006
01:40:21,992 --> 01:40:23,285
We're going to crash!

1007
01:40:27,957 --> 01:40:29,250
(SCREAMS)

1008
01:40:31,335 --> 01:40:32,670
(PANTING)

1009
01:40:35,881 --> 01:40:37,508
Water, water, water!

1010
01:40:37,591 --> 01:40:39,051
- WILLIE: Look! Look there!
- Water!

1011
01:40:39,218 --> 01:40:41,470
- WILLIE: Fire! You're on fire!
- Water, water!

1012
01:40:41,554 --> 01:40:44,473
- Look...
- Water, water.

1013
01:40:45,641 --> 01:40:47,434
Water, water.

1014
01:40:48,143 --> 01:40:50,229
Come on. Come on!

1015
01:41:03,867 --> 01:41:05,327
Let's go!

1016
01:41:09,540 --> 01:41:11,166
Run, run!

1017
01:41:11,250 --> 01:41:12,626
(SCREAMING)

1018
01:41:23,929 --> 01:41:25,306
SHORTY: Willie, look out!

1019
01:41:35,441 --> 01:41:36,567
No!

1020
01:41:36,650 --> 01:41:39,403
Head for the bridge. Go!

1021
01:41:40,696 --> 01:41:42,114
SHORTY: Come on, Willie. This way.

1022
01:41:55,502 --> 01:41:56,837
WILLIE: Oh, God!

1023
01:41:56,920 --> 01:41:58,922
Come on, let's go. Strong bridge.

1024
01:41:59,006 --> 01:42:01,842
Come on, let's go. Strong bridge.

1025
01:42:02,134 --> 01:42:03,969
Look, strong wood.

1026
01:42:04,803 --> 01:42:06,138
Come on!

1027
01:42:06,221 --> 01:42:07,514
Look!

1028
01:42:07,765 --> 01:42:09,475
WILLIE: Shorty!

1029
01:42:11,935 --> 01:42:13,937
Help! I'm falling down.

1030
01:42:16,607 --> 01:42:18,150
Help!

1031
01:42:20,027 --> 01:42:21,153
Not very funny.

1032
01:42:46,512 --> 01:42:47,846
Back!

1033
01:42:50,140 --> 01:42:51,225
(EXCLAIMING)

1034
01:42:53,185 --> 01:42:55,771
(CLAMORING)

1035
01:43:07,199 --> 01:43:09,451
(SCREAMING)

1036
01:43:13,539 --> 01:43:15,374
Welcome.

1037
01:43:16,667 --> 01:43:17,751
(SPEAKS HINDI)

1038
01:43:25,509 --> 01:43:26,593
(MOANS)

1039
01:43:27,886 --> 01:43:30,013
Let her go, Mola Ram.

1040
01:43:30,097 --> 01:43:34,059
You are in a position
unsuitable to give orders.

1041
01:43:34,560 --> 01:43:35,769
Watch your back!

1042
01:43:45,112 --> 01:43:46,697
You want the stones, let 'em go.

1043
01:43:51,326 --> 01:43:52,703
Let her go!

1044
01:43:52,911 --> 01:43:56,832
(LAUGHING) Drop them, Dr. Jones.

1045
01:43:56,915 --> 01:43:59,293
They will be found.

1046
01:43:59,376 --> 01:44:01,170
You won't.

1047
01:44:02,713 --> 01:44:04,298
(SHOUTS)

1048
01:44:04,381 --> 01:44:05,340
Indy!

1049
01:44:05,424 --> 01:44:07,009
Behind you!

1050
01:44:15,642 --> 01:44:17,770
Oh, shit.

1051
01:44:28,363 --> 01:44:30,032
Go on.

1052
01:44:31,116 --> 01:44:32,618
Go.

1053
01:44:41,752 --> 01:44:43,462
MOLA: Go on! Go on!

1054
01:44:44,546 --> 01:44:46,423
Get moving.

1055
01:44:50,177 --> 01:44:52,137
Shorty...

1056
01:44:52,346 --> 01:44:54,765
(SPEAKING CHINESE)

1057
01:44:57,684 --> 01:45:00,270
Hang on, lady. We going for a ride.

1058
01:45:02,064 --> 01:45:03,899
Oh, my God!

1059
01:45:05,734 --> 01:45:09,196
Oh, my God. Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

1060
01:45:09,655 --> 01:45:11,281
Is he nuts?

1061
01:45:12,157 --> 01:45:13,617
He no nuts.

1062
01:45:13,700 --> 01:45:15,285
He's crazy.

1063
01:45:15,619 --> 01:45:20,374
Mola Ram, prepare to meet Kali

1064
01:45:20,457 --> 01:45:22,209
in hell.

1065
01:45:23,293 --> 01:45:24,419
What are you doing?

1066
01:45:24,962 --> 01:45:26,338
(SCREAMING) You fool!

1067
01:46:13,844 --> 01:46:15,304
(MOLA SPEAKING HINDI)

1068
01:46:26,565 --> 01:46:28,275
Indy, cover your heart!

1069
01:46:28,358 --> 01:46:30,319
Cover your heart!

1070
01:46:30,944 --> 01:46:32,654
Oh, my God!

1071
01:46:32,738 --> 01:46:34,239
(MOLA CHANTING)

1072
01:46:42,581 --> 01:46:43,916
Oh, my God.

1073
01:47:05,896 --> 01:47:08,190
(BOTH SPEAKING HINDI)

1074
01:47:22,955 --> 01:47:24,581
(ORDERING IN HINDI)

1075
01:47:26,959 --> 01:47:28,293
- Look out!
- No!

1076
01:47:38,804 --> 01:47:40,138
(YELLING)

1077
01:47:44,226 --> 01:47:45,602
(GROANING)

1078
01:47:53,819 --> 01:47:55,320
No!

1079
01:47:59,783 --> 01:48:01,493
SHORTY: Come on. Let's go!

1080
01:48:02,411 --> 01:48:04,413
The stones are mine!

1081
01:48:05,497 --> 01:48:07,457
You've betrayed Siva.

1082
01:48:08,667 --> 01:48:11,336
(SPEAKING HINDI)

1083
01:48:11,712 --> 01:48:13,296
You betrayed Siva.

1084
01:48:14,798 --> 01:48:17,467
(SPEAKING HINDI)

1085
01:48:22,681 --> 01:48:24,099
You betrayed Siva!

1086
01:48:33,734 --> 01:48:34,776
(SCREAMING)

1087
01:48:56,214 --> 01:48:58,216
WILLIE: Well, it's about time.

1088
01:49:16,401 --> 01:49:17,903
MAN: Hold your fire.

1089
01:49:42,886 --> 01:49:43,929
(CHUCKLES)

1090
01:50:10,705 --> 01:50:12,040
(LAUGHING)

1091
01:50:33,562 --> 01:50:36,231
(ALL WHOOPING)

1092
01:50:41,486 --> 01:50:43,196
(EXCLAIMING EXCITEDLY)

1093
01:51:20,483 --> 01:51:22,694
We know you are coming back

1094
01:51:23,028 --> 01:51:25,864
when life return to our village.

1095
01:51:29,868 --> 01:51:36,374
Now you can see the magic
of the rock you bring back.

1096
01:51:36,666 --> 01:51:40,462
Yes, I understand its power now.

1097
01:51:46,218 --> 01:51:47,719
You could've kept it.

1098
01:51:47,802 --> 01:51:49,721
Ah! What for?
They'd just put it in a museum.

1099
01:51:49,804 --> 01:51:52,224
It'd be another rock collecting dust.

1100
01:51:52,307 --> 01:51:55,852
But then it would've given you
your fortune and glory.

1101
01:51:55,936 --> 01:51:57,687
Anything could happen.

1102
01:51:57,771 --> 01:51:59,981
It's a long way to Delhi.

1103
01:52:00,065 --> 01:52:01,149
No, thanks.

1104
01:52:01,233 --> 01:52:03,485
No more adventures with you,
Dr. Jones.

1105
01:52:03,568 --> 01:52:07,155
Sweetheart, after all the fun
we've had together?

1106
01:52:08,281 --> 01:52:11,326
If you think I'm going to Delhi with you,
or anyplace else

1107
01:52:11,409 --> 01:52:13,411
after all the trouble
you've gotten me into,

1108
01:52:13,495 --> 01:52:15,205
think again, buster!

1109
01:52:15,288 --> 01:52:17,707
I'm going home to Missouri
where they never feed you snakes,

1110
01:52:17,791 --> 01:52:20,502
before ripping your heart out
and lowering you into hot pits!

1111
01:52:20,585 --> 01:52:24,089
This is not my idea of a swell time!

1112
01:52:24,172 --> 01:52:27,050
Excuse me, sir. I need a guide to Delhi.
If you could...

1113
01:52:45,110 --> 01:52:46,528
(TRUMPETING)

1114
01:52:46,611 --> 01:52:48,613
(LAUGHING) Very funny.

1115
01:52:54,619 --> 01:52:56,121
Very funny.

1116
01:52:59,582 --> 01:53:00,583
Uh-oh!

1117
01:53:04,045 --> 01:53:08,216
(ALL CHEERING)

